Time":"2019-11-15T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"同男友住 佢呀媽開頭淺藍 老豆淺黃<br />\n呀媽之前會講下警察好辛苦 d示威者係咪收錢(聽d姨媽姑姐吹) 而家淺黃 明白係個仆街政府搞成咁<br />\n老豆就黃到橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我直頭懷疑佢有上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己果兩個就淺藍 但係佢地知我好黃 所以提都唔敢係我面前提 最多叫我小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係自己親戚whatsapp group都照串班藍絲親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班垃圾以為自己長輩就可以唔尊重人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239609732a2ff1bad254abbe1dc9582b5c37af3a","tid":1723764,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"我老母已經x 狗全家都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be80af2936819da5ab105bf3f6587c3f6bcb116f","tid":1723764,"uid":119442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"兩老深黃&gt;金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324e0b53434a187c47ed747afb8888afe7a30568","tid":1723764,"uid":59973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"冇轉過，keep住話搞咁多做咩，實鬥唔過共產黨，政府一定唔會妥協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有人死/重傷就話關佢撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebf2036e8458709e21671776f72b53697432459","tid":1723764,"uid":58687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31336ca093f5d40cca76c98922fa83208d4051b3","tid":1723764,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be80af2936819da5ab105bf3f6587c3f6bcb116f","tid":1723764,"uid":119442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T09:44:19.000Z","msg":"兩老深黃&gt;金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-